Level 0: Strategic Intent
  └── Mission Objectives
       └── Operational Constraints
       └── Strategic Policies

Level 1: Command Governance Layer
  └── Policy Controllers
       └── Rules Engines (Doctrinal Logic, ROE)
       └── Audit & Compliance Mechanisms
       └── Interoperability Standards (NATO STANAGs, etc.)

Level 2: Mission Command Layer
  └── Intent Parsing Agents
       └── Task Orchestration Modules
       └── Dynamic Authority Allocation (C2 Agility Nodes)
       └── Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

Level 3: Decision Support Layer
  └── Cognitive Assistants
       └── AI/ML Models (Predictive Analytics, COA Analysis)
       └── Human-Machine Interface (HMI)
       └── Data Fusion Engines (ISR Integration)

Level 4: Execution Control Layer
  └── Workflow Automation Systems
       └── Templated Mission Threads
       └── Execution Monitors (TTP Adherence)
       └── Effect Synchronization Tools

Level 5: Platform Interface Layer
  └── API Gateways / Middleware
       └── Edge Computing Nodes
       └── Robotic & Autonomous System Interfaces
       └── Secure Communications Modules

Level 6: Sensor-Actuator Layer
  └── ISR Sensors & Effectors
       └── Real-Time Telemetry Streams
       └── Feedback Control Loops
       └── Embedded Resilience Functions
